==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cornfield
<hw>Corn"field`</hw> <pr>(k?rn"f?ld`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A field
where corn is or has been growing; -- in England, a field of wheat, rye,
barley, or oats; in America, a field of Indian corn.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

